title: Huey Lewis is Poor Now
description:
Written by Alene Latimer
Starring Dan Hodapp, Lisa Kleinman, Avery Monsen, Kelly Hudson, Jonathan Marballi, Jon Bershad

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, March 3, 2014.

Filmed by Ryan Hunter and Curtis Raye.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
